{"tid":702314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇識/鍾意過好特別嘅女仔?","createTime":"2018-06-14T19:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T03:18:34.000Z","uid":189283,"like":29,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"089e20f86bb2ed248fda85f605dcce6a05f9a7c9","tid":702314,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T19:35:00.000Z","msg":"講緊會俾你種與眾不同感覺嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識過個女同學15幾普通樣<br />\n間唔中講下粗口<br />\n見佢都係同番女仔玩多<br />\n只係知讀書勁同鍾意動漫<br />\n感覺佢同一般港女係唔同嘅<br />\n有時仲有種霸氣 好難接近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最搞笑係身邊幾個兄弟都有好感/鍾意佢<br />\n但係冇人答到點解鍾意 仲要追極都追唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見個女仔連ig都冇 真心嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以講下依類型女仔<br />\n好好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d225ab3b837e8f61c0d1f2d30c10a535d42bf2d6","tid":702314,"uid":136900,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T19:37:37.000Z","msg":"毒撚一個帶少少social同氣場啫<br />\n我覺得唔追好過追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連ig都冇你唸下佢摺到"},{"pid":"0699b7a673a6d54078e956cebc7230a134cb6552","tid":702314,"uid":128863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T19:37:53.000Z","msg":"Girl crush"},{"pid":"24fd75c14605dd310abf756bfc24cb3f6f8a4212","tid":702314,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T19:38:52.000Z","msg":"有佢地都好特別<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/033839_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%